# 5. Verification Levels

| Level | Description |
|-------|-------------|
| **Level 1** | KPI-based estimation |
| **Level 2** | KPI + MBT55 evidence |
| **Level 3** | KPI + Evidence + Marketplace audit |
| **Level 4** | Third-party ESG verification |

